title: Georgia Fowler dresses up as Maleficent for Halloween Party New York
text:
She's used to wearing angel wings on the runway.

But Victoria's Secret Angel Georgia Fowler, 27, wore a very different style of wings on Sunday night when she dressed up as Angelia Jolie in Maleficent for a Halloween party in New York.

Taking to Instagram, the 27-year-old shared several snaps of herself looking the spitting image of Angelia in her dark mistress-inspired ensemble.

Doppelgänger alert! Victoria's Secret model Georgia Fowler, 27, (L) was the spitting image of Angelia Jolie (R) as she dressed up as Maleficent for Halloween in New York on Sunday

She simply captioned the photo: 'So you see, the story is not quite as it was told.'

Georgia was seen wearing a tight black latex outfit, thigh-high boots, a horned headpiece and giant feather wings.

The New Zealand-born model enhanced her facial features to resemble the evil character with a dark blush and eye shadow and red lipstick.

Striking: The New Zealand-born model enhanced her facial features to resemble the evil character with a dark blush and eye shadow and red lipstick

Uncanny: She looked every inch like the Disney character, wearing a black latex outfit, thigh high boots and giant wings

She documented the eventful night where she played in a foam pit and partied alongside fellow Victoria Secret models Sara Sampaio and Victoria Lee.

Earlier this month, the brunette beauty admitted to News Corp she doesn't like to overshare on social media and prefer to keep 'a bit' to herself.

'We're only showing a certain side of our lives (on Instagram),' Fowler said.

'I'm not posting the most unflattering photos of myself': Earlier this month, the brunette beauty told News Corp admitted she doesn't like to overshare on social media and prefer to keep 'a bit' to herself

'I'm not posting the most unflattering photos of myself. And sometimes, I might've taken 40 shots to get that one (selfie). It's all in the lighting.'

'I don't really want to show a thousand photos of me. It is still an image.'

Georgia rose to fame walking the Victoria Secret Fashion Show for the past three years.
description: She's used to wearing angel wings on the runway.
authors: David Wu For Daily Mail Australia
